        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2585375535" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12701788249672065182">A heart-wrenching account of true horror. All those innumerable people whose lives have been touched by this disaster... one can only hope that their wounds will get healed... <br/><br/>Maybe. <br/><br/>Someday.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review2585375535">
