<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/5586087-zinky-boys"><img alt="Zinky Boys: Soviet Voices from the Afghanistan War" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1348597622l/5586087._SY75_.jpg" />
